      public PlayerStats​(int ID, int minutes, int points, int rebounds, int assists, int steals, int blocks, int turnovers, java.lang.String fg, java.lang.String threePts, java.lang.String ft)
      Constructor that initialize the data members
      Parameters:
      ID - Team ID of the player to know which PlayerModel it is
      minutes - Time that the player spent to play
      points - Points that the player scored during the game
      rebounds - Rebounds that the player taked during the game
      assists - Assists that the player gived during the game
      steals - Steals that the player made during the game
      blocks - Blocks that the player made during the game
      turnovers - Turnovers that the player made during the game
      fg - Shoots that the player made and attempted during the game
      threePts - Three points shoots that the player made and attempted during the game
      ft - Free throws that the player made and attempted during the game
